 Billie Eilish分享了被鬼魂的经验：“我简直不敢相信” https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-shares-experience-of-being-ghosted-i-couldnt-believe-it-3764186?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=billie-eilish-shares-经验丰富的 -  i-couldnt-believe-itDamian Jones Mon, 10 Jun 2024 14:15:00 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3764186 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_eilish_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="比莉·艾利什" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_eilish_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_eilish_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_eilish_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_eilish_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_eilish_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_eilish_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>她的“打我辛苦而柔软”的世界巡回演唱会计划于今年秋天开始</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-shares-experience-of-being-ghosted-i-couldnt-believe-it-3764186">Billie Eilish的职位分享了被鬼魂的经验：“我简直不敢相信”</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上出现。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_eilish_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="比莉·艾利什" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_eilish_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_eilish_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_eilish_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_eilish_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_eilish_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_eilish_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">比利·埃里什（Billie Eilish）</a>谈到了她被幽灵的经历。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/billie-eilish-hit-me-hard-and-soft-review-tracklist-lyrics-3756826">Billie Eilish – 《Hit Me Hard and Soft》评论：大胆、精彩、更明亮</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位歌手兼作曲家最近发行了她的新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/billie-eilish-hit-me-hard-and-soft-review-tracklist-lyrics-3756826">“ Hit Me Hard and Soft”</a> ，他在他们的<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/sounds/brand/p0hhgmp6" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Miss Me</em></a> Podcast上向<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lily-allen">Lily Allen</a>和Miquita Oliver透露，这一事件发生在去年12月。</p><p>她说：“我当时，你死了吗？你真的死了吗？直到今天，[他]再也没有给我发短信。”</p><p> Eilish继续说：“是我也认识多年的人，并在电话中制定计划的那一天，这是我的地址，在下午3点在那里 - 再也没有听到他的消息。曾经。我简直不敢相信。” </p><figure style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/billie-eilish@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" /><figcaption class="wp-caption-text"> Billie Eilish信用：Arturo Holmes/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>这位歌手兼作曲家说，后来她看到他正在和别人约会。</p><p>她继续说：“我就像&#39;哦&#39;。但我不知道人们仍然这样做。我真的不知道人们这样做。”</p><p>在同一次采访中，埃里什还说，她“当我出名时失去了我所有的朋友”。</p><p>她说，她最好的朋友佐伊（Zoe）留在她身边，但她唯一的其他朋友是她的员工。</p><p> “那是我20岁生日，我记得在房间里看环顾，这是我所使用的人。她说，整个15岁以上。”她说。</p><p>尽管如此，她说她从那以后就与老朋友取得了联系，并在此过程中建立了一些新朋友。</p><p> Eilish补充说：“正好一年前，我与一群老朋友重新建立了联系，现在，我有很多朋友。我现在有一个船员！我真的可以为此哭泣。这是我发生的最伟大的事情。”</p><p>这位明星向<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-says-she-lost-all-of-my-friends-when-i-got-famous-3763992">艾伦（Allen）透露，她曾经为她2006年的首张单曲“微笑”的歌词哭泣，但它启发了她结交新朋友</a>。</p><p>她补充说：“我曾经想哭泣，因为我没有那样，因为我没有朋友。我记得我想我想这种感觉。我想听这首歌以各种方式与之相关，并听到有关朋友的句子，就像，我的朋友们通过了这首歌。”</p><p>同时，Eilish最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-billie-eilishs-self-directed-video-for-chihiro-3763459">分享了她的新专辑中的“ Chihiro”的自我指导的视频</a>。</p><p>她的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-announces-hit-me-hard-and-soft-world-tour-dates-in-uk-north-america-europe-and-australia-3751792">“打我辛苦和柔软”的世界巡回演出</a>计划于今年秋天开始。英国和爱尔兰的腿将于2025年7月举行，其中包括伦敦O2的六晚。 <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fbillie-eilish-tickets%2Fartist%2F2257710" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处找到剩余的门票</a>（英国/爱尔兰）和<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fbillie-eilish-tickets%2Fartist%2F2257710" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这里</a>（北美）。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-shares-experience-of-being-ghosted-i-couldnt-believe-it-3764186">Billie Eilish的职位分享了被鬼魂的经验：“我简直不敢相信”</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上出现。</p> ;
